mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on brown) announcing Stars for Muscular Dystrophy featuring Johnny Duncan, Carl Smith, Gary Stewart, and Sheb Wooley at the University of West Florida Fieldhouse on September 3. Poster features metal photoplates of the stars. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/50098/
